{
  "name": "PivotFilter",
  "summary": "<p>开发人员可以选择命名筛选器以供引用，因为索引不可靠。 <strong>DataField</strong> 属性指定要基于值筛选器的 PivotField。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中数据透视表的字段“id”的第一个筛选器的参数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtField = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtField.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第一张数据透视表的字段“score”的第二个筛选器是否是活动的。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;score&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Active</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>PivotFilter 应用于 <strong>PivotField</strong> 对象。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Active",
      "summary": "<p>当筛选的透视字段在数据透视表中，且数据透视表更新时会计算该筛选时，此属性返回 <strong>True</strong>。当筛选的透视字段不在数据透视表中，且对数据透视表计算没有影响时，此属性返回 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回指定透视筛选是否是活动的。只读 <strong>Boolean</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第一张数据透视表的字段“score”的第二个筛选器是否为活动的。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;score&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Active</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示工作表 Sheet1 中数据透视表字段“name”的第一个筛选器是否为活动的。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtFilter = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Active</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>table { word-break:break-all; </p>\n<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DataField",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>此属性仅适用于非 OLAP 数据透视表，可为值筛选提供作为筛选依据的<strong>值</strong>字段（值区域中的透视字段）。只读 <strong>PivotField</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示工作表 Sheet1 中数据透视表的字段“name”的第一个筛选器中作为筛选依据的值字段的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtFilter = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataField</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个数据透视表的字段“id”的第二个筛选器中作为筛选依据的值字段的公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtFilter = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    pvtFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataField</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;score*0.9&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "PivotField",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Description",
      "summary": "<p>说明字符串的最大长度为 255 个字符。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>为 <strong>PivotFilter</strong> 对象提供可选说明。只读 <strong>String</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示工作表 Sheet1 中数据透视表的字段“name”的第一个筛选器的可选说明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtFilter = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Description</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第一张数据透视表的字段“id”的第二个筛选器的可选说明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pvtFilter = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotFields</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotFilters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(pvtFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Description</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FilterType",
      "summary": "<p>下表列出了新的筛选器类型，以及对于每一个筛选器类型必须提供的参数和不可提供（不可用）的参数。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>xlPivotFilterType</th>\n<th>DataField</th>\n<th>DataCubeField (OLAP)</th>\n<th>Value1</th>\n<th>Value2</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>xlTopCount</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlBottomCount</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlTopPercent</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlBottomPercent</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlTopSum</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlBottomSum</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionEquals</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionDoesNotEqual</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionIsGreaterThan</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionIsGreaterThanOrEqualTo</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionIsLessThan</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionIsLessThanOrEqualTo</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionBeginsWith</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionDoesNotBeginWith</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionEndsWith</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionDoesNotEndWith</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionContains</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>必需</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>xlCaptionDoesNotContain</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\n<td>不可用</td>\